        "gg3BajX3jAe_text": "<p>If your skin is sensitive or reactive, \"new\" products can be scary. This hydrogel is cooling and ultra-gentle. <strong>It calms redness and smooths texture without the burning or stinging you get from harsh acids or chemical peels.</strong></p>",
        "gg7nCPFUnoD_label": "<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>",
        "ggCBkxNmyVl_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/4_19_d98f5845-c7b3-4c95-9220-3a1005101a44.png",
        "ggHIzq54zz__text": "5. The \"Transparency Test\"—You can see it working",
        "ggJ154sffaM_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/3_17_819119fe-b3c3-48ec-ad31-510efc54f0db.png",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Nicole Jenkins | UK<br>February, 2026</p>",
        "ggNzvrSfCrV_text": "2. One mask replaces a 5-step routine",
        "ggOGc25WEdF_text": "<p>We know you've probably been burned by viral gimmicks before. <strong>That’s why Nifora offers a 60-day satisfaction guarantee.</strong> If you don't see that \"glass skin\" bounce after your first few resets, you aren't stuck with it.</p>",
        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "6. It’s a \"Retinol Reset\" without the redness",
        "ggPDFGq_qm0_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/6_0a8af824-b65b-4bac-a023-6a6fffe74137.png",
        "ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text": "<p>You don’t have to guess if this is doing anything. The mask starts off as a thick, milky white. <strong>As your skin \"drinks\" up the ingredients, the mask becomes 100% transparent.</strong> When it’s clear, you know the nutrients have successfully moved from the mask into your skin. It’s the most satisfying visual proof you’ll ever see in your routine.</p>",
        "ggQPtwZzMvG_text": "4. It’s like a \"blanket\" that presses the glow into your skin",
        "ggTCZJLSmNN_text": "7. You can try the \"Glow\" Risk-Free",
        "ggUMmUh3HgV_label": "<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "Discover why 40,000+ busy moms are waking up to 'Glass Skin' and a refreshed glow with this 3-hour Bio-Collagen Reset",
        "ggUrpHf4v9e_text": "<p>We’ve all had those weeks where we look in the mirror and just feel... tired. <strong>This ritual is like an \"Undo\" button for dullness.</strong> It rebuilds that bouncy, healthy texture so you look like you’ve actually caught up on sleep, even when you’re running on empty.</p>",
        "ggWgTX2uyp5_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/5_15_8a238195-5ffd-4dd5-98fa-509792247a55.png",
        "ggZHuYgoc8x_text": "1. It actually stays put while you live your life",
        "ggd-lhkHKNI_text": "<p><strong>Note from the Warehouse:</strong> Because we make our collagen in small, high-potency batches, we frequently sell out during the winter months. If the link above works, it means we currently have stock ready to ship!</p>",
        "ggdTVwcLqP-_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/7_13_636aa2a6-6cbc-45bd-a61b-98142df7f556.png",
        "gggTy2IY0Ux_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/banner.png",
        "gghX7bwbbYs_label": "<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>",
        "ggj-b7-Ufnz_text": "Here are the 7 reasons why I’ve actually stuck with it:",
        "ggjPk9bJpvM_text": "3. No More \"Mom Face\" Fatigue",
        "gglrklurxwg_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_19_b34ea2ae-afc1-474f-ade8-9c8c7191df8c.png",
        "ggpHsxRi7jf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_16_0d534650-1dd4-469f-8722-a77acfb893c9.png",
        "ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_12_50193272-513c-40d6-8a84-526e705d46b1.png",
        "ggvDN5djePx_text": "<p>Most masks are just \"wet paper\" that slides off the second you stand up. This Bio-Collagen mask acts like a second skin. You can do the laundry, cook dinner, or even sleep in it without a single drip. It’s <strong>\"Passive Skincare\"</strong>, it does the hard work while you’re busy being a mom.</p>",
        "ggxpEEAWkOo_text": "<p>Most creams just sit on the surface and evaporate into the air. This mask acts like a little blanket for your face. It creates <strong>an airtight seal that \"presses\" the hydration deep into your pores</strong> instead of letting it dry out on your pillowcase.</p>",
        "ggxwUzin72S_text": "<p>Stop overcomplicating things. You don't need a shelf full of serums that don't sink in. <strong>One Nifora session provides deeper hydration than a whole week of standard moisturizers.</strong> It saves you time, money, and cabinet space.</p>",
        "ggy5Uy9f896_text": "<p>Most moms don’t skip skincare because they don’t care. They skip it because there’s no energy left at the end of the day. <strong>Between work, kids, and everything in between, long routines just aren’t realistic; even when your skin clearly needs help.</strong></p><p><br>That’s why more busy moms are turning to overnight skincare that works in the background, while they rest.</p>"
      },
